				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I 2 boxed the wand camp in the Deep last night with my Shaman.  First spawn dropped the cloak and the second dropped the wand!  It's a 15 minute respawn so it's not bad at all.
<br />

<br />
It was an easy camp, but the tricky part is getting past any see invis mobs that are in the way on the way down without some form of lull or pacification.  I basically had to stop and kill the see invis along the way.  Thankfully most of the Horror model mobs don't see invis so it's not too bad once you get past the invisible bridge.
<br />

<br />
Although if you're solo and you get 4-5 mobs on your pet at once in there it can be a challenge regardless of your level or AAs.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=24305" target="_blank" class="postlink">Kalamos Somalak</a></span>
