				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This probably IS solable by a 65 with 12 AA, but will involve some luck (ie, be ready to gate).  I did this a few weeks ago at ~24 AA (scm2/scf2 + pet hold) and DPOC but BARELY had enough mana to keep the pet alive.  I did this with the air pet initially, and had to gate on the last of a 4-mob group (a walker came by at the wrong @#$@ing moment and grabbed the only one of the group that HADN'T yet aggro'd, but I'd already killed several).
<br />

<br />
When I came back, I was able to run all the way since I assumed that no new see invis mobs were there.  I pulled up earth and killed the last mob from the first group, then moved forward.  I used earth because CC was just too much of an issue.
<br />

<br />
The second attempt went well, I ran completely OOM on the very last mob at the camp site but was able to yo-yo the pet letting DPOC heal him.  Oh, complete side note, DPOC air pet on /pet sit /pet hold is wonderful for letting chanters med up when doing the hedge quest by making thelin stand still...</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
